{"tid":1911163,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"卑詩省老婦確診染病　加拿大官員：懷疑她在香港受感染","createTime":"2020-03-05T06:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T07:36:02.000Z","uid":212626,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4660cb250a74ab3f7e131c0317c3e60a15eda316","tid":1911163,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:59:23.000Z","msg":"加拿大卑詩省一名曾經到香港旅遊的81歲老婦，感染新型冠狀病毒，目前在溫哥華一間醫院接受隔離治療，情況危殆。衛生官員表示，患者本身有長期病患，早前組團到印度及香港旅遊，上星期回國，數日後出現病徵。官員指印度只有零星病例，根據患者出現病徵的時間，懷疑她在香港受感染，已將個案通知香港衛生部門，並追蹤同團的人。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大至今確診34宗新型冠狀病毒個案，有13宗在卑詩省。國防部宣布，軍方為疫情大流行進行預備工作，會暫停非緊急派遣任務，如有需要將會派往疫區，協助撤僑。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1271670&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1271670%26csid%3D261_341&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq%2F7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=91dea2f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1271670&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"0cb831858c9cc1aab9e91dde872bf3477871fb88","tid":1911163,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解唔係印度"},{"pid":"15b9c0e94e43567c83781f69a1fe96bb042e6161","tid":1911163,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7063299f056d0ec4216602f78ee1a43f67312ec2","tid":1911163,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:03:45.000Z","msg":"懷疑她在香港受感染<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de1818a185090dc0d1f0d1efa037b5535d4b6cc","tid":1911163,"uid":264426,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:05:28.000Z","msg":"話唔埋可能去過北角呢"},{"pid":"69184f3d084c04165fa825f7f0be38c602c837e4","tid":1911163,"uid":21262